An article by Xi Jinping, general secretary of the Communist Party of China Central Committee, on strengthening cultural confidence and developing a great socialist culture in China will be published Sunday in the 12th issue of the Qiushi Journal this year. The article by Xi, also Chinese president and chairman of the Central Military Commission, stressed that without strong cultural confidence and a prosperous cultural sector, national rejuvenation will not be realized. 
